    "text": "Home Loan Quality Transparency Act of 2021 \n\nThis\u00a0bill expands requirements for public disclosures by depository institutions\u00a0and credit unions regarding mortgages and home equity lines of credit. Specifically, institutions originating fewer than 500 mortgage loans or open-end lines of credit annually are no longer exempt from certain financial reporting."
